data.description: Enjoy entertaining in this sprawling ranch home which boasts over 3,200 square feet of living space. You will not be disappointed when you walk in and see the  the large living/dining room windows which let in an abundance of natural light. The cathedral ceilings add to the bright and airy room which features a brick wall with fireplace.  The equipped kitchen with solid oak cabinetry has plenty of storage space for all your culinary needs and an eating bar.  Finishing off the first floor you will find 3 sizeable Br's with extra closets and a full bath with double sinks and tiled shower.  The open staircase leads to an immense family room with second fireplace.  An additional suite is offered in the lower level.  With a full kitchen, bath, 2 bedrooms and living room...the possibilities are endless...mother-in-law suite, rental, etc. The lower level is a walk out and the suite has its own entrance. Sitting on almost an acre with all city services!  large deck with above ground pool, patio, and 16 x 12 shed w/electric  Many updates including Roof '17, furnace '22, C/A '19, WH '20, garage door and opener '23, outside painted '23, plumbing updates '24, new pool liner and pump '19  Don't miss out on this unique home!!
